Name:           toipe
Version:        0.4.1
Release:        0
Summary:        Yet another typing test, but crab flavoured
License:        (Apache-2.0 OR Apache-2.0 WITH LLVM-exception OR MIT) AND (Apache-2.0 OR MIT) AND (MIT OR Unlicense) AND MIT
URL:            https://github.com/Samyak2/toipe
